title: Nakhid challenges Europe's power, wealth in pitch for FIFA
text:
> Sports Nakhid challenges Europe's power, wealth in pitch for FIFA Former Trinidad and Tobago midfielder David Nakhid, who last week submitted his candidacy to FIFA to stand in February's emergency presidential election, attends a training session for children, in Beirut, Lebanon, Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015. (AP Photo/Bilal Hussein)
